#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:394
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:541
msgid ""
"When checked, matches against ALL of the pipeline's category_map values "
"instead of the list below. Leave unchecked to name only specific categories "
"(e.g. just the ones you want to exclude), which is usually what you want "
"when this condition is guarding a single category node rather than the whole"
" seed."
msgstr ""
"勾选此选项时，将与管道中所有 category_map "
"值进行匹配，而非仅匹配下方的列表。若不勾选，则仅指定特定类别（例如仅指定要排除的类别），当此条件用于保护单个类别节点而非整个种子时，通常需要采用这种方式。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:400
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:547
msgid "Categories:"
msgstr "类别："

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:402
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:549
msgid "category name"
msgstr "类别名称"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:404
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:551
msgid ""
"Categories this condition matches against. Matching is OR across this list: "
"the condition succeeds if ANY of these categories occupies a qualifying rank"
" position (see Rank range) with a high enough score (see Min confidence)."
msgstr ""
"此条件匹配的类别。匹配方式为列表中的 OR：如果这些类别中的任何一个在合格的排名位置（参见排名范围）并拥有足够高的分数（参见最小置信度），则条件成立。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:415
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:562
msgid ""
"Position in the classifier's own ranked output to start checking, where rank"
" 1 is the single category the classifier considers most likely, rank 2 the "
"next most likely, and so on. Min/Max together define an inclusive window of "
"positions to inspect -- they are NOT a confidence range."
msgstr ""
"在分类器自身的排序输出中开始检查的位置，其中 rank 1 是分类器认为最可能的单一类别，rank 2 是次可能的类别，依此类推。Min/Max "
"共同定义一个包含的检查位置区间——它们不是置信区间。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:421
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:568
msgid "Min:"
msgstr "最小:"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:428
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:575
msgid ""
"End of the rank-position window (inclusive). Min=Max=1 (the default) only "
"checks the classifier's single top guess, so a listed category ranked 2nd or"
" lower will NOT match even if it's a strong secondary signal. Widen this "
"(e.g. 1-3) to catch a category anywhere in the top N guesses."
msgstr ""
"排名位置窗口的结束（含）。Min=Max=1（默认）仅检查分类器的单个最高预测，因此列出的类别排名第2位或更低时，即使它是强烈的次要信号，也不匹配。将其扩大（例如"
" 1‑3）可捕获位于前 N 条预测中的任何类别。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:434
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:581
msgid "Max:"
msgstr "最大:"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:437
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:584
msgid "Rank range:"
msgstr "排名范围："

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:445
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:592
msgid ""
"Minimum score (0-1) a listed category must have at its rank position to "
"count as a match. The default of 0.0 is the LEAST strict setting -- it "
"accepts any score, so only rank position and category membership decide the "
"match. Raise this (e.g. 0.3-0.5) to require the classifier to actually be "
"confident, rather than matching on a near-zero score that happened to land "
"in the rank window."
msgstr ""
"最低分数（0‑1），列出的类别在其排名位置上必须达到的分数，才能算作匹配。默认值 0.0 "
"是最宽松的设置——接受任何分数，因此只有排名位置和类别成员资格决定匹配。提高此阈值（例如 "
"0.3‑0.5），可以要求分类器真正有信心，而不是在几乎为零的分数恰好落入排名窗口时匹配。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:452
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:599
msgid "Min confidence:"
msgstr "最小置信度:"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:454
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:601
msgid "Negate (match when categories are NOT found)"
msgstr "否定（未找到类别时匹配）"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:457
msgid ""
"Unchecked (default): matches when a listed category IS found in the rank "
"window with enough confidence -- a positive detection. Check this to flip "
"that, so the condition matches when NONE of the listed categories qualify. "
"Useful as a guard sub-condition alongside RelatedImageCondition / "
"BaseStemMatchCondition on an AND node, where True already means \"clear to "
"generate\" for those -- e.g. 'generate banana only if not already Cherry', "
"without needing to wrap this condition in a separate NOT composite (which "
"the sub-condition picker here doesn't support nesting anyway, and which "
"would otherwise cost a second, separate, non-cached classifier evaluation)."
msgstr ""
"Unchecked "
"(default)：当在排名窗口中以足够的置信度找到列出的类别时匹配——正向检测。勾选此项可颠倒逻辑，使条件在**没有**任何列出类别符合时匹配。可作为与"
" RelatedImageCondition / BaseStemMatchCondition 在 AND 节点上配合使用的守护子条件——此时 True"
" 已经意味着“可以生成”——例如“仅在未生成 Cherry 时生成 banana”，无需将此条件包装在单独的 NOT "
"复合中（此子条件选择器本身不支持嵌套，否则会导致第二次、独立、未缓存的分类器评估）。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:468
#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:609
msgid "Negate:"
msgstr "取反:"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:484
msgid "(no classifiers)"
msgstr "（无分类符）"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:536
msgid "Audio classifier:"
msgstr "音频分类器："

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:604
msgid ""
"Unchecked (default): matches when a listed category IS found in the rank "
"window with enough confidence -- a positive detection. Check this to flip "
"that, so the condition matches when NONE of the listed categories qualify."
msgstr "未选中（默认）：当在排名窗口中以足够的置信度找到列出的类别时匹配——正向检测。勾选此项可翻转逻辑，使条件在没有任何列出类别符合时匹配。"

#: ui/compare/classifier_pipeline_editor_qt.py:625
